name: Yada Kenyada
description: Hi am new to this and am Yada by name am looking for a decent and responsible man for a matured relationship. I am a woman and a young girl all rolled into one. I am intelligent and resourceful, and will sometimes make you laugh and shake your head. Sweet and loving are words often used by others to describe me. You will find me refreshingly honest with a positive and optimistic attitude. I enjoy the magic of love and am very amorous and passionate. I’d like to one day find myself in a genuine, loving and exclusive relationship.
